<BaseLayout title="Legal and Privacy Requests | CourtScope" noindex={true}><section class="hero"><div class="prose-width"><p class="eyebrow">Protected request</p><h1>Legal and privacy requests</h1><p class="lede">Use this channel for sealed or expunged records, privacy risk, intellectual-property concerns, or a legal removal request.</p></div></section><section class="section"><div class="prose-width"><div class="notice warning">Do not send passwords, Social Security numbers, full birth dates, medical records, or unnecessary identity documents by ordinary email.</div><div class="card"><h2>What to include</h2><ul><li>The affected CourtScope URL or dataset release.</li><li>The exact record, field, or content at issue.</li><li>The legal or privacy basis for the request.</li><li>An official source, order, or verification path where applicable.</li><li>A safe way to contact you.</li></ul><a class="button" href="mailto:info@courtscope.org?subject=Legal%20or%20privacy%20request">Email the protected request</a><p class="help">CourtScope records the request, preserves an audit trail, and separates legal/privacy review from ordinary corrections.</p></div></div></section></BaseLayout>